highlights.text: “Dance Ka Bhoot” by Pritam, Arijit Singh, and Amitabh Bhattacharya is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Delhi, up 36 spots at #58.
“Rasiya” by Pritam, Shreya Ghoshal, and TUSHAR JOSHI is the highest new entry on Top Songs Delhi at #30.
Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Delhi. “Kesariya” is the highest at #1.
“Excuses” by AP Dhillon, Gurinder Gill, and Intense has been on Top Songs Delhi the longest, at 51 weeks straight.
